recordTypes.description:
No person shall do any grading, stripping, clearcutting, or otherwise disturb an area unless a valid grading permit is received from the Zoning Enforcement Officer. The following are the only exceptions:
\ta. \tagricultural use of land other than the creation of new pasture land;
\tb. \tan approved development where the disturbed area is cumulatively less than one-half acre;
\tc. \ta single family residence that is not part a subdivision.
